<script type="text/javascript">
  try {
    const entries = {};
    try {
      const mpDataElements = document.querySelectorAll('meta.mpSizeChart-formData');
      mpDataElements.forEach(element => {
        const key = element.name.split('-')[1];
        const content = (element.hasAttribute('data-no-parse') || false) ? element.content : JSON.parse(element.content || '[]');

        if (entries.hasOwnProperty(key)) entries[key] = [...entries[key], ...content];
        else entries[key] = content;
      });
    } catch (e) {
      console.log('An error when get mp data', e.message);
    }

    const [{
      dataMetafields = {},
      cacheCampaign = {},
      template,
      collectionId,
      campaignsContent = [],
      productId, productTitle, productType, productVendor, productTags,
      isDesignMode = false
    }, collectionsName, collections]
      = [entries, [], []];

    

    const initData = () => ({
      ...dataMetafields,
      campaignsContent,
      product: {
        id: +productId,
        title: productTitle,
        type: productType,
        vendor: productVendor,
        tags: productTags
      },
      template,
      collectionsName,
      collections,
      collectionId,
      isDesignMode
    });

    if (!window?.AVADA_SC) window.AVADA_SC = initData();
    window.AVADA_SC = {...window.AVADA_SC, ...initData(), cacheCampaign};

  } catch (e) {
    console.error('Error assigning Size Chart variables', e);
  }
</script>

  #shopify-section-temp<script>
document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
    const carousel = document.querySelector("#carousel-template--23861633745239__text_with_icons_TLKHaY");
    if (!carousel) return;

    const items = carousel.querySelectorAll(".text-with-icons__item");
    const totalItems = items.length;
    let index = 0;
    let isAnimating = false;

    function isMobile() {
        return window.innerWidth < 1000;
    }

    function slide() {
        if (!isMobile() || isAnimating) return;

        isAnimating = true;
        const currentItem = items[index];
        index = (index + 1) % totalItems;
        const nextItem = items[index];

        // Move next item in position
        nextItem.style.display = "flex";
        nextItem.style.position = "absolute";
        nextItem.style.transform = "translateX(100%)"; // Start off-screen right
        nextItem.style.transition = "transform 0.5s ease-in-out";

        setTimeout(() => {
            // Slide current out
            currentItem.style.transform = "translateX(-100%)";

            // Slide next in
            nextItem.style.transform = "translateX(0)";

            setTimeout(() => {
                currentItem.style.display = "none"; // Hide previous
                currentItem.style.position = "relative"; 
                isAnimating = false;
            }, 500); // Matches transition duration
        }, 50);
    }

    function initializeCarousel() {
        if (isMobile()) {
            items.forEach((item, i) => {
                item.style.display = i === 0 ? "flex" : "none";
                item.style.position = "relative";
                item.style.transform = "translateX(0)";
            });
            setInterval(slide, 4000);
        } else {
            items.forEach(item => {
                item.style.display = "flex"; // Keep desktop layout the same
                item.style.position = "relative";
                item.style.transform = "translateX(0)";
            });
        }
    }

    initializeCarousel();
    window.addEventListener("resize", initializeCarousel);
});
</script>

<script>
document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
    const carousel = document.querySelector("#carousel-template--23861633745239__text_with_icons_TLKHaY");
    if (!carousel) return;

    const items = carousel.querySelectorAll(".text-with-icons__item");
    const totalItems = items.length;
    let index = 0;

    function isMobile() {
        return window.innerWidth < 1000;
    }

    function switchItem() {
        if (!isMobile()) return; // Only apply on mobile

        items.forEach((item, i) => {
            item.style.display = i === index ? "flex" : "none";
        });

        index = (index + 1) % totalItems; // Loop through items
    }

    function initializeCarousel() {
        if (isMobile()) {
            items.forEach((item, i) => {
                item.style.display = i === 0 ? "flex" : "none";
            });

            clearInterval(window.mobileSliderInterval);
            window.mobileSliderInterval = setInterval(switchItem, 3000); // Change every 3 seconds
        } else {
            clearInterval(window.mobileSliderInterval);
            items.forEach(item => {
                item.style.display = "flex"; // Keep desktop layout as-is
            });
        }
    }

    initializeCarousel();
    window.addEventListener("resize", initializeCarousel);
});

</script>
